      "section_id": "para_57",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "3.  (1)  There  is  hereby  established  a  fund  to  be  known  as \nthe  National  Trust  Fund  which  shall  be  specified  in  and \nthe  Financial \nthe  Second    Schedule \nincorporated  into \nProcedure  Act  1957 [Act  61].",
